<h3>Taxonomy Version Review Administration</h3>
<%= render partial: 'taxonomy_version_reviews/main_tab/system_status' %>
<h4>Workflow</h4>
<ol>
  <li/>Choose a taxonomy
    <ul>
      <li/><%= link_to("All taxonomies",
                       search_path(query_string: '*',
                                   query_target: 'tree'),
                       class: "with-underline",
                       title: "Retrieve a list of all taxonomies") %>
      <li/><%= link_to("Accepted taxonomy",
                       search_path(query_string: 'accepted:', query_target: 'tree'),
                       class: "with-underline",
                       title: "Retrieve the accepted taxonomy") %>
    </ul>

    <li/>Choose an (unpublished) taxonomy <b>version</b> for review
    <ul>
      <li/><%= link_to("Unpublished taxonomy versions",
                       search_path(query_string: 'unpublished:',
                                   query_target: 'tree_versions'),
                       class: "with-underline",
                       title: "Retrieve all unpublished taxonomy versions") %>
    </ul>
  <li/>Create a review record for the version
    <ul>
      <li/>Use the "Review" tab for a taxonomy version
    </ul>
  <li/>Retrieve the review record
    <ul>
      <li><%= link_to("Taxonomy version reviews",
                      search_path(query_string: '*',
                                  query_target: 'taxonomy_version_reviews'),
                      class: "with-underline",
                      title: "Retrieve all unpublished taxonomy version review records") %>
      <li/>Taxonomy version "Details" tab lists and links reviews
    </ul>
  <li/>Set up a review period 
    <ul>
      <li/>Use the "Periods of Review" tab for a taxonomy version review
      <li><%= link_to("Taxonomy version review periods",
                      search_path(query_string: 'any:',
                                  query_target: 'taxonomy_version_review_periods'),
                      class: "with-underline",
                      title: "Retrieve all taxonomy version review period records") %>
    </ul>
  <li/>Allocate reviewers to the review period 
  <li/>Read review comments 
  <li/>End a review period
  <li/>End a review
</ol>
<h5>Workflow Suggestion</h5>
Open the Editor in at least 2 tabs of your browser
<ul>
  <li>keep this administration tab open in one of the browser tabs,
  <li>use the other browser tab for the work
</ul>
